        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "ABS Global Smart School - Korattur"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Suman Ramanathan"
          },
          "datePublished": "2022-10-31",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi All,\n\nTo be very frank! I am posting this review only based on my experience as a parent of a Kindergarten Kid:\n\nPros:\n1. Great vision towards kids education and extra curricular activities.\n2. Teachers are very friendly, caring and supportive with kids. Regular activities are conducted.\n\nCons:\n1. False commitments and lack of response from Management\n2. Incomplete infrastructure\n-> No indoor play area for Kindergarten kids (this makes lack of engagement for kids during rainy season) and only classroom/projector sessions will be there during rainy days which leads to their zero learning.\n-> Montessori method of teaching was committed but there has been no progress on it and its been more than 6 months now.\n->unsafe/shaggy pathway from gate to class rooms\n\nI decided to admit my kid in this school was only because of the promises made on indoor/outdoor play area setup and Montessori ways of teaching that every children should learn & experience to lead their life and learning but it is very disappointing that promises are not being kept. There has been slow and nil progress in action towards the infrastructures. I am sure that this would be every parent’s expectation from school.\n\nLooking forward to witness timely differences!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        }
      ]
